## Defaults

- **UI work:** Read `pump-tma-design-system` → `pump-tma-ui-ux`. Top nav + mobile bottom bar — no left sidebar.
- Verify library APIs via Context7 — do not guess versions.
- Match patterns in `apps/web/src/` before new libraries or UI primitives.
- **No shadcn/MUI** — use `globals.css` classes and `pump-*` tokens.
- **Icons:** Material Symbols via `PumpIcon` + `@/lib/pump-icons` (not Lucide/Font Awesome).
- Dev: `npm run dev` (web :3012) · `npm run dev:admin` (:5174). Layout: `docs/repo-structure.md`.
